# API Contract Rules

## Base URL

```
http://localhost:3000/api
```

## Response Format

ALL API responses must follow this format:

```typescript
interface ApiResponse<T> {
  success: boolean;
  data?: T;
  error?: string;
  message?: string;
}
```

## Endpoints

### Users

```
GET    /api/users           # Get all users
GET    /api/users/:id       # Get user by ID
PUT    /api/users/:id       # Update user
```

### Groups

```
GET    /api/groups          # Get all groups
GET    /api/groups/:id      # Get group by ID
POST   /api/groups          # Create group
```

### Expenses

```
GET    /api/expenses                # Get all expenses
GET    /api/expenses?groupId=:id    # Get expenses by group
GET    /api/expenses/:id            # Get expense by ID
POST   /api/expenses                # Create expense
```

## Request/Response Examples

### Create Group

**Request:**
```json
POST /api/groups
{
  "name": "Weekend Trip",
  "description": "Our amazing weekend",
  "memberIds": ["user-1", "user-2"]
}
```

**Response:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "id": "group-123",
    "name": "Weekend Trip",
    "description": "Our amazing weekend",
    "memberIds": ["user-1", "user-2"],
    "createdBy": "user-1",
    "createdAt": "2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z",
    "updatedAt": "2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z"
  },
  "message": "Group created successfully"
}
```

### Create Expense

**Request:**
```json
POST /api/expenses
{
  "groupId": "group-1",
  "description": "Dinner",
  "amount": 120,
  "currency": "USD",
  "paidBy": "user-1",
  "splitBetween": ["user-1", "user-2", "user-3"],
  "category": "Food"
}
```

**Response:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "id": "expense-123",
    "groupId": "group-1",
    "description": "Dinner",
    "amount": 120,
    "currency": "USD",
    "paidBy": "user-1",
    "splitBetween": ["user-1", "user-2", "user-3"],
    "date": "2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z",
    "category": "Food",
    "createdAt": "2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z",
    "updatedAt": "2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z"
  },
  "message": "Expense created successfully"
}
```

## Error Handling

**Error Response:**
```json
{
  "success": false,
  "error": "Group not found"
}
```

## CORS

Backend enables CORS for all origins (development only).
